{
  "stem": "4963.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And told them not to worry, that they will take care of me when I come back.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they were actually sent out on a Thursday, and on a Friday or Saturday, the Germans marched in.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, when the Germans marched into Lithuania, I was in summer camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- What was the summer camp about?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Was it a-- describe it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a Zionist camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I believe it was Habonim, and we were all from school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We belonged to this group of-- Zionist group.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so they had a summer camp and that's where I went.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So, immediately, when the Germans came in, and I remember them coming in, they opened up the camp and, you know, started to-- were thinking of annihilating Jewish-- I mean, Jewish children, all in-- that's the last thing they ever needed.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, what I saw was the Germans with their-- I remember, with their hats, with their hard hats over them, with-- with guns, and-- what do you call them?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- that they beat the children-- you know, you know, that-- the-- [INAUDIBLE], whatever they-- you call them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember them opening up the doors and saying, out, everybody out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so we were permitted to just take whatever we could carry with us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they started marching us from place to place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This went on for about, I would say, four or five days.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was in the summer and it was hot, I remember.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we marched in the middle of the street.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were like five people in a line.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were many children there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they didn't feed us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was really my first encounter with hunger.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
